itunes:title: 10 Things I've Learned From Being A Salon Owner
title: 10 Things I've Learned From Being A Salon Owner
description:
In this episode Jessi opens up about the up's and down's of being a business owner and talks about 10 things she has learned since opening her salon 5 years ago! Reviews, comparisons, hard clients, booth rent vs.commission; she talks about it all!
